title: SC EP:75 Looking back over the last 75 shows
itunes:title: SC EP:75 Looking back over the last 75 shows
description: Tomorrow night is our 75th show. We invite everyone to call in and share their encounter, comments or whatever you want. This is an opportunity to ask questions on stuff we have talked about in the past or future plans.
